item.title: IMAGE FORGERY DETECTION APP
item.description: Developed an Android application to detect fake human images.It differentiates GAN-generated face-images from real face-images.Methodology involved training ResNet-50 model on a publicly available datasetThe proposed architecture had an accuracy of 90%The trained model was deployed on a Django-based API and made available via Android application.
